<div class="challenges-summary">
  <!-- Header image -->
  <%= image_tag("waste.jpeg", class: 'challenges-header-img') %>
  <div class="image-overlay"></div>
  <div class="challenges-desc">
    <h1>CLEAN</h1>
    <p>Conventional cleaning products are laden with unhealthy chemicals. Cleaning may not be fun,
      but it’s even worse when the ingredients in your products leave harmful chemical residue in place of
      dirt and grime. You know it’s not safe to take a swig of that bright blue surface cleaner, but why are
      we okay to have it covering the space we come into contact with all day?!</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="all-challenges">
  <div class="challenges-header">CHALLENGES</div>
  <div class="accordion" id="challenge-accordion">

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
        <h5 class="mb-0">
          <!-- Challenge header  -->
          <button class="accordion-toggle btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
            ASSESS YOUR CLEANING PRODUCTS
          </button>
        </h5>
      </div>

      <!-- Collapsible challenge body -->
      <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#challenge-accordion">
        <div class="card-body container">
          <div class="row">
            <div src="" class="col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag("placeholder.png", size: '100x100') %>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body-text col-md-10">
              <div>
                More than 80,000 chemicals are unregulated by the federal government, including most of those
                in common household cleaning products. Chances are that your conventional cleaning products contain
                substances which, when inhaled or absorbed through the skin, cause serious health problems.
                Gather all of the cleaning and laundry products in your home, and use EWG's Guide to Healthy
                Cleaning to check their health ratings.
              </div>

              <div class="learn-more">
                <p class="learn-more-header">Learn more</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <a class="learn-more-text" href="https://www.ewg.org/guides/cleaners">Resource</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="challenge-duration">
                <p class="learn-more-header">How long do you want to take the challenge for?</p>
                <form>
                  <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="3">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                      <select class="form-control" id="inputInterval">
                        <option>Choose interval</option>
                        <option>day(s)</option>
                        <option>week(s)</option>
                        <option>month(s)</option>
                      </select>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </div>

              <button class="get-started-btn">
                GET STARTED ON THIS CHALLENGE!
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
        <h5 class="mb-0">
          <button class="accordion-toggle btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
            MAKE YOUR OWN CLEANING SOLUTIONS
          </button>
        </h5>
      </div>
      <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#challenge-accordion">
        <div class="card-body container">
          <div class="row">
            <div src="" class="col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag("placeholder.png", size: '100x100') %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
              <div>Cleaning should not be an expensive or an unsafe process. Skip browsing the cleaning aisles
                and make your own cleaning solution. You can make your own with as little as one ingredient!
                And it'll save you more than 50% of money spent on buying those cleaning products from the cleaning aisle.
              </div>
              <div class="learn-more">
                <p class="learn-more-header">Learn more</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <a class="learn-more-text" href="http://trashisfortossers.com/category/cleaning/">Zero waste</a>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <a class="learn-more-text" href="https://www.lisabronner.com/category/house-cleaning/">Dr. Bronner house cleaning</a>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <a class="learn-more-text" href="https://wellnessmama.com/6244/natural-cleaning/">DIY</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="challenge-duration">
                <p class="learn-more-header">How long do you want to take the challenge for?</p>
                <form>
                  <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="3">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                      <select class="form-control" id="inputInterval">
                        <option>Choose interval</option>
                        <option>day(s)</option>
                        <option>week(s)</option>
                        <option>month(s)</option>
                      </select>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </div>

              <div class="get-started-btn">
                GET STARTED ON THIS CHALLENGE!
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
        <h5 class="mb-0">
          <button class="accordion-toggle btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
            UPCYCLE OLD CLOTHES
          </button>
        </h5>
      </div>
      <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#challenge-accordion">
        <div class="card-body container">
          <div class="row">
            <div src="" class="col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag("placeholder.png", size: '100x100') %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
              <div>
                There's no need to buy new cleaning rags. Just use old clothes, like t-shirts, cotton dresses,
                or cotton PJs, that you don't wear anymore! Use them as is or cut them up. You'll save money
                and lengthen the lifetime of the clothing piece.
              </div>
              <div class="learn-more">
                <!-- Add content here if more resources are added -->
              </div>

              <div class="challenge-duration">
                <p class="learn-more-header">How long do you want to take the challenge for?</p>
                <form>
                  <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="3">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                      <select class="form-control" id="inputInterval">
                        <option>Choose interval</option>
                        <option>day(s)</option>
                        <option>week(s)</option>
                        <option>month(s)</option>
                      </select>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </div>

              <div class="get-started-btn">
                GET STARTED ON THIS CHALLENGE!
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
